Step 4: Magic Merge dialog + Conflict Overview sidebar

New components:
  - MagicMergeDialog.tsx: modal showing resolved/remaining counts with undo
  - ConflictOverview.tsx: sidebar grouping conflicts by status, click to jump

Changes:
